sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant V as Vehicle / simulator
  participant API as FastAPI
  participant DB as PostgreSQL

  V->>API: POST /telemetry
  API->>DB: BEGIN (single transaction)
  API->>DB: upsert vehicle
  API->>DB: insert telemetry_event
  API->>DB: INSERT zone_counters ON CONFLICT DO UPDATE entry_count + 1
  API->>DB: detect and insert anomalies (5 deterministic rules)
  alt status == fault
    API->>DB: fault transition (lock vehicle, cancel mission, open maintenance)
  end
  API->>DB: COMMIT (all of it lands or none)
  API-->>V: 201 accepted
